{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stay hidden among the crowd and defeat your opponents before getting spotted, or you risk not surviving in this <strong>party game</strong> where you need to mix <strong>stealth</strong>, <strong>speed</strong>, and <strong>tactics</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with 2 to 10 players, either locally or online, across 7 different game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/game_modes.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/target.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the <strong>Target</strong> mode, each round presents a target that all players must find and kill. There is always one less target than the number of players, meaning the slowest to eliminate their target gets eliminated. The rounds continue until there is only one player left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/target_gif.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/battle_royale.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Battle Royale</strong>, players must stay inside a shrinking zone. If they go outside they are eliminated. The zone will keep moving and shrinking, and players can use their lightsaber to eliminate enemies. The last player standing wins the round.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/br_gif.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/domination.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Domination</strong> is a tug-of-war mode where players work together to push an energy bomb into the opponent\u2019s territory. The more players are in the zone, the faster they push the object. Players can eliminate enemies with lightsaber, and respawn 3 seconds after being killed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/domination_mode.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/race.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Race</strong> mode, the goal is to reach the finish line first. Players have 3 shots to eliminate characters they believe are controlled by other players. Each player is randomly assigned one of four abilities, and random events may occur in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/race_gif.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/zombie.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Zombie</strong> mode, players must activate 4 computers while avoiding being hit by zombies. If a player is hit, they become zombified and can no longer activate computers, but they can infect other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/zombie_mode.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/green_light.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Green Light</strong> mode, players must reach the finish line. But when the lights are on, players must stop moving to avoid being spotted, because the NPCs will never move. Players can use their 3 shots to eliminate characters they believe are other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/greenlight_gif.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/gold.png?t=1732112230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Gold</strong> mode, golden statues appear each round, and players must touch a statue to survive. There is always one less statue than the number of players, and the player who fails to touch a statue is eliminated. The rounds continue until there is only one player left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/extras/gold_mode.gif?t=1732112230\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Drone killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/3db9de277d5786eac49ea13413c1a0d7522cb92a.jpg"},{"name":"Beam Me to Victory!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/4309c1c11aecb248bca655def08f03dd514555e1.jpg"},{"name":"Death ray !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/faf52358cae387150532fe4f2d570223efe3315b.jpg"},{"name":"NPCs: 1, Players: 0","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/f404bcedbca5b6044857df6f2d75cb1032f74e89.jpg"},{"name":"360 Quickscope","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/7a30e5dd7a5d9f8fee313d65aa3f8466c9229492.jpg"},{"name":"Last One Standing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/3901afdd67bc9424b73cf4accfd74d3d8bd0c001.jpg"},{"name":"The floor is lava","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/4ea6b232cfaa6a1578df6b40ff2bf2970a86c405.jpg"},{"name":"Blind shot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/6116dd42c204702ec31ff4620dc6879d56b93312.jpg"},{"name":"One vs Zombies","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/33ba8c46aac3c7002d45558d4287c5beb8e05c6a.jpg"},{"name":"No Rush to Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3047320/bc6f32f6994611019f6258b2e75d3ce281973d51.jpg"}],"total":12},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3047320?t=1732112230","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1732112230","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/3326861f844eabc866eaad4910e9a39381478bbe/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732112230","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047320/3326861f844eabc866eaad4910e9a39381478bbe/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732112230","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split